oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Johnny Bush Job No. 16157
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: Accounting; Hatch Show Print (Firm);
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Typed invoice for an order placed by Johnny Bush for 100 two color window cards announcing Johnny Bush at the Roundup Club in Skidmore, Texas on May 3. Receipt indicates agreed price, size, order quantity, shipping location and description. To view the poster for this order see https://digi.countrymusichalloffame.org/digital/collection/hatch3/id/39861.
